# 5 Most Important Answers (Yaad Kar Lo)

✅ Load Balancer → Traffic distribute karta hai

✅ Redis → Fast cache hai, RAM me data store karta hai

✅ API Gateway → Single entry point for microservices

✅ Kafka/RabbitMQ → Asynchronous communication

✅ Microservices → Independent deployment aur scaling

### 1-Minute Interview Introduction

> "System Design me main scalability, reliability aur performance par focus karta hoon. High traffic applications ke liye Load Balancer, API Gateway, Redis Cache, SQL Server aur Kafka/RabbitMQ use karta hoon. Large enterprise applications me Microservices architecture prefer karta hoon kyunki services independently deploy aur scale ho sakti hain."

Ye answer .NET/C# Developer interviews me bahut strong impression create karta hai.
